1
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,560
Are you new in town?

2
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,560
I suppose.

3
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:19,079
Another poor soul.

4
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:21,770
What brings you to the government office?

5
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:22,960
To deliver money.

6
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,240
Come in first.

7
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,280
Master, Gesang.

8
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:13,280
Clear sky, divine earth.

9
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:16,520
Old immortals, reveal the true forms.

10
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:21,200
Immortals, help me open my magic eyes.

11
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:24,520
Demons and monsters, reveal your true forms.

12
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:34,820
Those who disobey shall be captured.

13
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:40,160
A powerful demon.

14
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,760
Master.

15
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,680
Our men are ready.

16
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,160
Let's go.

17
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:00,360
Please wait here, everyone.

18
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:02,040
I will go in and report first.

19
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,480
Everyone.

20
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:17,839
I am Gu Yanqing, the Deputy Magistrate of Tangcheng.

21
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,480
What brings you here?

22
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,680
Deputy Magistrate.

23
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,280
We are here to deliver money.

24
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:28,520
This...

25
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,370
What is the meaning of this?

26
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,880
This is ill-gotten wealth.

27
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:37,680
Please accept it according to the procedures, Deputy Magistrate.

28
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:39,140
Return them to the people.

29
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:42,960
There are still such noble people in this world.

30
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:45,720
What a pity.

31
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:47,000
A pity?

32
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,370
It's easy for you to come in,

33
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,680
but hard to get out.

34
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,200
Deputy.

35
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,760
I know there is something strange about Ercheng.

36
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:59,840
Tell us, and we might be able to help.

37
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,680
Even the government office can do nothing.

38
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:06,160
How can the three of you help?

39
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:08,640
If it's about bandits or civil affairs,

40
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:10,300
I wouldn't want to interfere.

41
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,960
But if it's monsters causing trouble,

42
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,620
I can actually be of some help.

43
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:17,220
You've already run into them.

44
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,600
Did you promise to stay?

45
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,290
You must have promised to stay.

46
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:29,200
Otherwise, how could you still be alive?

47
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:31,770
The three of us killed all those monsters.

48
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:36,240
Please don't boast.

49
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:38,040
We stayed at Miaoren Bathhouse last night.

50
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:40,500
That Wen Jiuniang was a monster in disguise.

51
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:43,240
We have slain all the monsters in the building.

52
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:49,770
Please step into the inner hall to talk, Masters.

53
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,120
Please.

54
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,660
Please have a seat.

55
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,560
You have everything here.

56
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:53,040
Did you really kill the demon in Miaoren Tang?

57
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,480
See for yourself if you don't believe us.

58
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,400
Heaven always leaves a way out.

59
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,960
The Heavens have finally opened their eyes.

60
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:02,640
Are you an official from the Sitian Bureau?

61
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,400
No.

62
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:12,280
Although I am not a Sitian Bureau official,

63
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:14,480
I do know a thing or two about subduing demons.

64
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,410
What exactly happened in Ercheng?

65
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:18,570
Please tell us, County Deputy.

66
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:22,440
That was three years ago.

67
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:27,640
Three years ago, Ercheng was not as prosperous as it is today.

68
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,560
There were only hot springs here,

69
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,440
and it was a remote area.

70
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:32,760
Until that day,

71
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:35,080
when a beautiful woman came to the city,

72
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:37,280
named Ruixi.

73
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,640
Look at that lady. She's so beautiful.

74
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:50,280
She's so pretty.

75
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:52,120
Yeah, so attractive.

76
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,040
What a beautiful lady.

77
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,840
What is she doing in our Ercheng?

78
00:07:58,640 --> 00:07:59,600
Look at that box.

79
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,130
It looks very heavy.

80
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,600
What's in it?

81
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,120
I don't know.

82
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,880
Please inform the county magistrate.

83
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:31,800
I have something to ask of him.

84
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,640
Greetings, Your Honor.

85
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,480
State your name.

86
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:41,440
I am Rongxi,

87
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,960
from Jiangnan.

88
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,330
I just arrived here,

89
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:47,320
and wish to do some business.

90
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:49,280
Ercheng has free trade.

91
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:51,640
If you wish to do business,

92
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,280
report to the Supervisory Bureau,

93
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,040
follow the legal procedures,

94
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:56,640
and you can open your shop.

95
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:58,340
Why come to the county office?

96
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:01,600
That would be true for a small business.

97
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,280
But what I intend to do

98
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:05,640
is something that will greatly change

99
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:07,760
Ercheng's commerce.

100
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:12,040
Naturally, I must inform the Magistrate.

101
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:16,640
What kind of business do you want to do, my lady?

102
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,200
Open it.

103
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,560
Wow.

104
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,720
So much silver.

105
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:40,280
Look at all this silver.

106
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:51,200
What is the meaning of this, my lady?

107
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:56,040
I want to start a money-lending business in Ercheng.

108
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:57,500
Money lending?

109
00:09:58,000 --> 00:10:00,480
There are already many pawnshops in Ercheng.

110
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:02,640
How do you plan to

111
00:10:02,640 --> 00:10:04,640
improve Ercheng's trade with this?

112
00:10:05,800 --> 00:10:08,930
Pawnshops require jewelry and fine silk as collateral.

113
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:11,800
Poor families without jewelry or fine silk

114
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,680
naturally cannot borrow money.

115
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,040
From now on,

116
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:17,440
all merchants and commoners in Ercheng

117
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:19,400
can borrow money from me.

118
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,480
For foreign trade

119
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:21,880
or city construction,

120
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,680
I guarantee sufficient funds.

121
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:27,360
And no collateral is required.

122
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,440
That is so nice.

123
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:32,000
That is so nice.

124
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:34,480
So Ruixi is a good person.

125
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,440
Didn't the County Deputy say

126
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,640
that Ruixi is a demon?

127
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:39,060
How can demons be good?

128
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,840
Humans can be good or evil.

129
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,570
Why can't there be good demons?

130
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:49,500
County Deputy, please continue.

131
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:53,040
At first,

132
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:55,960
Magistrate Shen also thought it was a good thing.

133
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:59,200
If you do this, miss,

134
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,200
for you,

135
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:03,360
there's no guarantee for the silver you loan out.

136
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:06,160
I trust the people of Ercheng.

137
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:11,960
But if the borrowers really can't repay the silver,

138
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,240
what then?

139
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:15,300
Do you really have no conditions?

140
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,120
No.

141
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:19,000
But there is only one catch when borrowing from me.

142
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:21,600
The interest will be slightly higher.

143
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:23,560
I don't need collateral.

144
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:27,560
It's understandable that the interest rate is a bit higher,

145
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:30,080
right, My Lord?

146
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,660
I will let you give it a try.

147
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:37,040
I now permit you to open a money-lending shop in Ercheng.

148
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:38,280
From today on,

149
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:41,680
any merchants or commoners in Ercheng in need

150
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:43,600
can go to you to borrow money.

151
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:45,440
This matter is of great consequence.

152
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:48,080
It concerns the livelihood and commerce of Ercheng.

153
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,840
Do not act recklessly.

154
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:52,280
You must abide by the law

155
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:56,080
to help keep Ercheng's trade routes open and the people prosperous.

156
00:11:56,760 --> 00:12:00,840
If you hike up the interest rates and exploit the people,

157
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:04,240
don't blame me for being strict with the law.

158
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:11,160
Then I thank you on behalf of the people of Ercheng, My Lord.

159
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:35,520
Ping Jie, Qiang Haihui.
